@section installation Installation

---
@subsection installation-from-binary Binaries
- Docker
  - `docker pull docker.semio.xyz:5000/libsemio-ros`
- .deb for Debian Sid:
  - Available in latest release: https://github.com/semio-ai/semio_ros/releases/latest

@subsection installation-from-source Source Code
- GitHub repo: https://github.com/semio-ai/semio_ros
  - `git clone https://github.com/semio-ai/semio_ros.git && cd semio_ros && git submodule init && git submodule update`
- Zip/tarball
  - Available in latest release: https://github.com/semio-ai/semio_ros/releases/latest

